facts on the infections of sexual transmission
what are the main diseases of sexual transmission ?
between the incidence of bacteriano origin are the syphilis , the chlamydia and the gonorrea .
the incidence of vírico origin more arise are the aids , the virus the human papilloma , the herpes mutilation or the hepatitis .
the ladillas and the sarna are between the airborne incidence parasites .
what are the main groups of those ?
the syphilis and the gonorrea are with more often in men are sexual relations with other men .
the institute robert koch part of the basis of the least four of every five cases of syphilis registered in germany have their origin in a sexual contact between men .
in the case of the heterosexuales adults the diseases of sexual transmission more arise are the infections chlamydia , tricomonas , the virus the human papilloma , candidiasis ( ) hongo and the gonorrea .
the infection the hiv between the heterosexuales adults the country is relatively small ; not however , approximately the 20 % of the new infections hiv are in this group .
between the people , the infections chlamydia are much more arise that in others groups of population .
that european surveys , three quarters of all the infections affect to people of between 15 and 25 years .
in our country , the virus the human papilloma also adds to the diseases more arise between the youth .
how has there the number of infections ?
not all the diseases of sexual transmission are subject to compulsory declaration .
according the institute robert koch , the number of infections syphilis has doubled their figure of 1.697 cases in 2001 to 3.698 cases in 2011 .
the number of new infections hiv is a downward trend since 2007 .
in 2011 registered approximately 2.700 cases .
is of a tenth least part in the previous year .
what symptoms show that is of a venérea disease ?
the infectious diseases can cause úlceras in the area mutilation , deal the orinar , flow , abdominal pain , as ampollas or verrugas .
to often not cause pain or have other symptoms and that not that .
how can one protect ?
the condoms can reduce the risk of infection , but not are protection the hundred hundred .
some such players of diseases of sexual transmission also can be to through of infections suciedad and physical contact .
this reason , the experts proposed must regularly to medical examinations , on all if change with often of sexual couple .
