messenger : the nasa discover ice in mercury
the probe messenger has found evidence of the existence of ice in mercury .
probably the layer of ice have a thick of to 20 metres .
the nasa , the agency american space , has has evidence of the existence of ice in mercury .
to despite of dealt the planet more have the sun , there also there helada water , as and as from of three studies published the thursday in the magazine was &quot; bamst &quot; .
